00:02:47.720 --> 00:02:49.660
from Psalm 119,

00:02:49.660 --> 00:02:51.339
as really kind of a springboard

00:02:52.020 --> 00:02:53.100
into this three part series.

00:02:53.100 --> 00:02:55.179
And next Wednesday evening,

