00:03:16.419 --> 00:03:17.979
to examine our own lives and say,

00:03:17.979 --> 00:03:21.500
Lord, I really desire to see God do something.

00:03:21.500 --> 00:03:24.220
I don't wanna just see what we can do.

00:03:25.479 --> 00:03:28.259
