00:03:37.139 --> 00:03:38.139
And I know that we have,

00:03:38.139 --> 00:03:40.860
listen, I believe that God's still on his throne, amen.

00:03:40.860 --> 00:03:42.580
And God is still on his throne.

00:03:42.580 --> 00:03:45.839
God, he is the same yesterday, today and forever.

00:03:45.839 --> 00:03:47.479
And you read in the Bible

00:03:47.479 --> 00:03:49.600
