00:04:10.919 --> 00:04:14.679
We need to be able to keep record in our own lives

00:04:14.679 --> 00:04:18.519
in this calendar year of look at what God did.

00:04:18.519 --> 00:04:19.880
When we come to Psalm 119,

00:04:19.880 --> 00:04:23.000
