00:30:56.520 --> 00:31:05.960
this way. God did it. Lord, I pray that You'd help us to be humble. Help us, Lord, to be

00:31:05.960 --> 00:31:12.440
available, to be used of Thee. Help us to be doers of the Word. Help us, Lord, to seek

00:31:12.440 --> 00:31:17.860
You and obey You. Thank You for the privilege of corporate prayer. And I pray that as we

00:31:17.860 --> 00:31:23.280
enter into this time of our service, as we have opportunity to pray together, I pray,

00:31:23.280 --> 00:31:28.080
Lord, that You'd bless and we'll thank You for it. In Christ's name we pray. Amen.

